name: Osteole Batemanni
description:
--Fig.14--
Osteole Batemanni is a creature from Madriu, an exoplanet located 358 light years from earth, orbiting the star Arcalis.  
On the great fields of Madriu, there is no separation between life and death, or the material and spiritual world, so Osteole is a creature that celebrates death as much as life, showing all the beauty of both cycles.
